title: BRIEF-Altia net profit rises to 2.2 million euros in H1
text:
BRIEF-Altia net profit rises to 2.2 million euros in H1 Sept 18 
Sept 18 Altia Consultores SA : 
* H1 revenue 32.4 million euros ($36.8 million) versus 24.2 million euros year ago 
* H1 EBITDA 4.0 million euros versus 2.6 million euros year ago 
* H1 net profit 2.2 million euros versus 1.3 million euros year ago 
* Sees reaching results expected in business plan 2014-2015
